+*       rw-flag: 0, write; 1, read
+*       read:  echo 10005           > rw_reg ---read reg 0x00-0x05
+*       write: echo 000050102030405 > rw_reg ---write reg 0x00-0x05 as 01,02,03,04,05
+*  Get result:
